                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/5746" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0863</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8279 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信视像国际化之东瀛战记：跨境并购的运作与决策</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The internationalization of Hisense V.T. in Japanese market: Operation and decision in cross-border M &amp; A</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">刘端，朱茜，王雅轩，冯琼，张婧</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">湖南大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信视像科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">家电行业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">营销部门/资本运营部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信视像；TVS；跨境并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Hisense V.T.; TVS; Cross border M &amp; A</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">海信集团着眼全球竞争和企业长远发展，推出“大头在海外”的国际化战略布局，其电视业务子公司——海信视像的全球化布局也随之全面加速推进。通过跨境并购，海信视像进一步掌握技术纵深、扩大市场规模、提升品牌影响力，实现产品高端化、品牌全球化。本案例以海信视像并购日本老牌家电企业东芝旗下的电视板块子公司TVS为主线，详细描述了海信视像在跨境并购各阶段所面临的问题，重点阐述了海信视像在跨境并购关键时点所做的决策与资本选择，包括目标公司的选择、交割价格的确定、支付方式的选择等。通过分析本案例，旨在引导案例使用者思考企业如何在跨境并购时选择恰当的并购标的、制定合适的收购方案，并给其他实施跨境并购的企业提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">Focusing on the global competition and long-term development of the company, Hisense Group has launched an international strategic layout of &quot;big heads overseas&quot;. The global layout of its TV business subsidiary, Hisense V.T., has also accelerated in an all-round way. Through cross-border mergers and acquisitions, Hisense V.T. has further mastered the depth of technology, expanded market scale, enhanced brand influence, and achieved high-end products and brand globalization. This case takes the acquisition of TVs by Hisense V.T. as the main line, describes in detail the problems and choices faced by Hisense V.T. in each stage of acquisition, and focuses on the selection of target company, acquisition pricing and payment method in the process of acquisition. Through the analysis of this case, the purpose is to guide the case users to analyze how to choose an appropriate M &amp; A target, formulate the appropriate acquisition plan, and thus provide reference for other enterprises to implement cross-border M &amp; A.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《公司理财》、《高级财务理论与实务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司并购、企业并购</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021-12</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
